reviewText: This is another great video in the never ending Land B4 Time DVD series. Luckily, they are high quality shows that my son really enjoys. The characters are great & the stories are cute! AAAAA++++++ DVD for the entire family to watch!

reviewText: I loved the full length feature as a child and my daughter (4) loves it too.  This DVD includes multiple stories that she doesn't seem to get tired of.  If your kids like dinosaurs, they're sure to like this too.
